  show ?thesis1 ?thesis2 unfolding p q map_pmf_rep_eq using refl trans
    by(auto 4 3 simp add: measure_distr reflpD AE_measure_pmf_iff intro!: measure_pmf.finite_measure_mono_AE dest!: pq elim: transpE)
